ass=3D"sdf">Marion Maneker</a></u>=E2=80=A6</i><br/><br/></p><ul style=3D"m=
argin:0;color:#000000;font-size:16px;line-height:30px;margin-top:0;margin-b=
ottom:0;list-style-type:square;mso-special-format:bullet"><li><i>Sotheby=E2=
=80=99s layoff fears</i>: The esteemed auction house has been trying to kee=
p a lid on its impending job cuts ever since the May sales ended. The chatt=
er in the art world is that 25 percent of the London staff could be exited,=
 eventually. But that may just be nerves running through the industry as th=
e European market rebalances between London and Paris, as I <u><a href=3D"h=
ttps://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dQMnVu=
UVB0blFueEpnRGJSVnJ0ST0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wdWNrLm5ld3MvbG9uZG9ucy1hcnQ=
tbWFya2V0LWxvc3MtaXMtaG9uZy1rb25ncy1nYWluLz91dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249RHJ5K1Bvd2Rlci=
