x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Have we finally, at=
 long last, reached the Paramount Global endgame? It=E2=80=99s increasingly=
 looking that way. On Friday, word leaked that the special committee of the=
 Paramount board of directors had recommended to <b>Shari Redstone</b> the =
deal proposed by a consortium led by <b>David Ellison</b> of Skydance Media=
 and <b>Gerry Cardinale</b> of RedBird Capital, after the group sweetened i=
ts bid over the course of the last week. On Sunday afternoon, the <i>Journa=
l</i> <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1l=
